# Corbind's Product and Services

## Corbi
- A platform for writers and their readers. We value writers with autonomy and freedom, while keeping content accessible and suitable for new generations.
- We operate in the gap between the serial book market (The book is edited, produced, and delivered. It features professional authors and best-selling books. It has a high barrier to entry, requiring a proven audience, a network of connections, financial investment, and other factors) and the traditional book market (The book is published and followed in chapters. Composed of amateur and hobbyist authors. It has a low barrier to entry, but no path to professional growth.) with the goal of working alongside the writer to guide them towards professionalism and major global publishers.
- See @corbi.mdc to learn more